name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Recently, many netizens posted on social media that they were fired by their company on the first day of work after the Chinese New Year. Some netizens also said that on the first day of work, they found out that the company had closed down after they arrived at the company.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Some netizens found that a surveillance camera was installed every 10 meters in a section of Songshan Road in Luoyang City.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
On the evening of February 19, Messi posted a video to clarify and denied the false news that had been circulated online. He said that he was not unable to play in the Hong Kong friendly match due to political reasons, but because he suffered from adductor inflammation, which prevented him from playing, and he had already felt unwell before the first friendly match in Saudi Arabia. The day before the friendly match in Hong Kong, China, he tried to train, but was unable to play due to physical reasons. It was not until a few days later that he felt a little better that he played for a while in Japan.
Messi said that it was important to clarify these false news, and he has always had special feelings for Chinese fans.
